name: Bacon Asparagus & Camembert Stuffed Chicken Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Preheat oven to 180c and add baking paper to an oven-safe baking dish.
Place thighs (skin side down) in baking dish and spread open.
Place cheese and 2 asparagus spears on each thigh.
Start with short cut piece of middle bacon and place on top of cheese and asparagus. Wrap around thigh. Repeat with all pieces.
Season with salt and pepper and bake in the oven for 30 to 40 minutes.
